<p class="ql-align-center">小时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">躲被窝、蹲茅坑、逛地摊时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你看过<strong>《世界未解之谜》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么<strong>百慕大三角</strong>绝对是童年噩梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书上说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船和飞机一旦踏入这三角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会消失</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">军队和科学家查半天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连条毛都找不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查不出原因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201109/0de50beeb17646b9acdd8f8c77ba95fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
